{"schema_id":"pm.auto_decisions.schema.v1","decision_id":"dec-2026-02-26-context-injection-defaults","timestamp_utc":"2026-02-26T06:40:10Z","scope":"plans.context_injection","inputs_hash":"8b54038289300b72463ccf4407d23206a866fc9c33116352a5ff074615ba2e52","decision":"set_context_injection_defaults_and_budgets","rationale":"The Context Injection feature must be deterministic and low-bloat by default. Default all three injectors ON (Parent Summary, scoped AGENTS.md chain, Attempt Journal) to preserve intent and prevent repeated failures; enforce small, fixed budgets (parent_summary hard-capped to 10 lines; AGENTS.md authoring-time budgets 8KB/80 lines/6 headings) so instruction files remain light and promotion cannot accrete wiki content; attempt journal injection remains single-most-recent only, hard-capped to 4KB or 60 lines (truncate deterministically if exceeded); strict mode defaults to WARN-only to avoid blocking runs unexpectedly.","applied_to":["Plans/agent-rules-context.md","Plans/Contracts_V0.md","Plans/assistant-chat-design.md","Plans/orchestrator-subagent-integration.md","Plans/Orchestrator_Page.md","Plans/Run_Graph_View.md","Plans/FinalGUISpec.md","Plans/Project_Output_Artifacts.md"],"contract_refs":["PolicyRule:Decision_Policy.md\u00a72","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#InstructionBundleAssembly","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#AttemptJournal","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#ParentSummary","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#PromotionRules","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#AgentsMdLightEnforcement","ContractName:Plans/Contracts_V0.md#ContextInjectionToggles","ContractName:Plans/agent-rules-context.md#FeatureSpecVerbatim"]}
