{"schema_id":"pm.auto_decisions.schema.v1","decision_id":"dec-2026-02-26-assistant-memory-subsystem-defaults","timestamp_utc":"2026-02-26T16:33:07Z","scope":"plans.assistant_memory","inputs_hash":"1d7484a0483c63ffcabc90c7bbe376c72974871434d0913553ccf79a98ee4d38","decision":"set_assistant_only_memory_storage_and_prompt_injection_defaults","rationale":"Assistant memory integration requires deterministic defaults for physical store separation, capsule budget, retrieval cap, half-life decay, and strict Assistant-only access boundaries so memory remains low-bloat, project-scoped, and non-conflated with rules. Defaults were fixed in one SSOT and referenced by dependent plans to avoid duplication and ambiguous runtime behavior.","applied_to":["Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md","Plans/assistant-chat-design.md","Plans/storage-plan.md","Plans/rewrite-tie-in-memo.md","Plans/agent-rules-context.md","Plans/00-plans-index.md","Plans/auto_decisions.jsonl"],"contract_refs":["PolicyRule:Decision_Policy.md\u00a72","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#1-capability-boundary","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#2-physical-storage-layout","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#9-deterministic-defaults"]}
{"schema_id":"pm.auto_decisions.schema.v1","decision_id":"dec-2026-02-26-evidence-backed-gists-verification-defaults","timestamp_utc":"2026-02-26T17:21:23Z","scope":"plans.assistant_memory","inputs_hash":"be5756c92cf01b6781f13b6a126005e95773636fcadefc436132eb7cdc60222d","decision":"set_evidence_backed_gists_verification_and_injection_defaults","rationale":"Set deterministic verification/injection defaults for Evidence-Backed Gists: Verified-only capsule + retrieval injection is ON by default; unverified auto-save remains enabled (assistant.memory.auto_save_unverified=true) but does not relax injection gating; GUI manual Verify must be evidence-backed (no arbitrary Verified marking without recomputable EvidenceRefs); AutoRunBoundary and AutoMilestone triggers are each rate-limited to 1 invocation per run and deduplicated (embed_text_hash / (gist_id,evidence_ref)) to prevent duplicate writes. Capsule budget (350 tokens) and max injected items (5) remain as previously set by dec-2026-02-26-assistant-memory-subsystem-defaults.","applied_to":["Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md","Plans/assistant-chat-design.md","Plans/auto_decisions.jsonl"],"contract_refs":["SchemaID:pm.auto_decisions.schema.v1","PolicyRule:Decision_Policy.md\u00a72","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#5-verification-and-triggers","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#6-prompt-injection-contract","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#7-gui-and-maintenance","ContractName:Plans/assistant-memory-subsystem.md#9-deterministic-defaults","ContractName:Plans/assistant-chat-design.md#17-context--truncation","ConfigKey:assistant.memory.auto_save_unverified","ConfigKey:assistant.memory.capsule_budget_tokens","ConfigKey:assistant.memory.max_injected_items_per_turn"]}
